topics.body:
Man; shit's going down in Ferguson.

You know how a while back I was talking about that dude that a police officer shot who was unarmed?  Shit hit the fan.


Basically the state law enforcement and a ton of federal agents have pretty much stepped in cause the situation there was rapidly deteriorating and there's enough evidence that the cops are not exactly. . err squeaky clean that state law enforcement are relieving the local officers of duty temporarily and enforcing the law themselves instead.  It's so bad right now that cops are beating the shit out of reporters and yelling racial slurs at people on camera.

It's apparently one big racially motivated powder keg that someone lit and the state police are going looney toons right now trying to blow the fuse out before it explodes.

Tl:dr; man shit got stepped in big time.
